name: Drumbeat
description:
Part of a series of automatic drawings. These drawings are started with no initial ideas in mind. Drawing is a very spontaneous process and lines are created very quickly. I react as I go to what I see, trying to make interesting shapes and compositions. The work posses a movement or flow which emphasizes a feeling, this piece is dancing to the drumbeat.

Resolution: 1125 x 1500 (150 dpi)
Format: JPG
Color: RGB
File Size: 1.27 MB
Media: Hand drawing, digitally colored.
Date of Creation: 2021
